name: Dumbblle
description: Using dumbbells will work more muscles around the shoulders and chest than using a barbell because they're forced to keep the weights.

name: Push-up
description: It's a Good Full Body Workout - By working on a large number of muscles in your body, push-ups help tremendously for a fitter you.

name: Chin-Up
description: As a result, chin-ups better work the muscles on the front of your body, like your biceps and chest, while pull-ups are more effective at targeting your back.

name: Bench-Press
description: The bench press, is a weight training exercise in which the trainee presses a weight upwards while lying on a weight training bench.

name: Bent-over-row
description: A bent-over row is a weight training exercise that targets a variety of back muscles. Which ones are targeted varies on form.

name: Deadlift
description: The deadlift is a weight training exercise in which a loaded barbell or bar is lifted off the ground to the level of the hips.
